      <title>CME在24小时交易中测试Google的区块链技术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/cme-tests-google-s-blockchain-technology-in-24-hour-trading-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CME Group Inc.正在测试Google Cloud的区块链技术，因为它试图在全球往返全天交易的全球转变中改善市场基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/cme-tests-google-s-blockchain-technology-in-24-hour-trading-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:56:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼说，加拿大希望与特朗普在贸易谈判中“认真”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/carney-says-canada-wants-to-get-serious-with-trump-on-trade-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）说，他的顶级内阁部长正在与白宫官员接触，并希望就贸易进行“认真的”谈判，因为美国贸易伙伴为唐纳德·特朗普总统的下一份关税打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/carney-says-canada-wants-to-get-serious-with-trump-on-trade-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>并购基本上已经停止了，凯恩·安德森（Kayne Anderson）的拉比尔（Rabil）说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-25/m-a-has-basically-stopped-kayne-anderson-s-rabil-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯恩·安德森（Kayne Anderson）首席执行官艾尔·拉比尔（Al Rabil）说，衰退或艰难着陆的几率被绝大多数公众低估了“彭博公开利益”。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-25/m-a-has-basically-stopped-kayne-anderson-s-rabil-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:52:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着国际货币基金组织信号延迟有关新协议的会谈，塞内加尔欧洲邦遭到了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/senegal-eurobonds-fall-as-imf-signals-delay-in-talks-on-new-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔美元的债券在一位国际货币基金组织官员表示，关于新贷款计划的会谈可能会延迟，因为它评估了上一个政府对政府债务规模的错误陈述，可能会推迟有关新贷款计划的会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/senegal-eurobonds-fall-as-imf-signals-delay-in-talks-on-new-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:37:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能（Glencore）削减煤炭产量以阻止价格低落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/glencore-to-cut-coal-production-to-halt-prolonged-price-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Glencore PLC表示，它正在切割计划的煤炭生产，这是世界上最肮脏的燃料中最大的托运人，希望停止价格长时间的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/glencore-to-cut-coal-production-to-halt-prolonged-price-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:11:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当交易者对关税风险做出反应时，美国铜命中率很高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-copper-hits-record-high-as-traders-react-to-tariff-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约Comex Exchange的铜值期货飙升至记录，因为交易者的价格可能会对关键的工业金属征收高额进口关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-copper-hits-record-high-as-traders-react-to-tariff-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 13:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
