    <item>
      <title>股票交易者消除弱消费者信心：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易者看上去超过估计的经济数据，股票上升，市场从有史以来的股票抛售之一中扩大了反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 22:34:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国政府机构领导的ESG市场不断增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/a-1-8-trillion-esg-market-is-being-driven-by-the-us-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可持续债务市场的1.8万亿美元角正在违背更广泛的经济低迷状态，因为投资者扣除了美国政府机构的主要支持，即使唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领导了绿色撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/a-1-8-trillion-esg-market-is-being-driven-by-the-us-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
